{"tid":2119560,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"路由器裝VPN全屋裝置即刻加密 3大私隱安全設定你要知","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T06:29:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"886a300462f2a3e85a3a0e558480eab2aafce24d","tid":2119560,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:20:43.000Z","msg":"網絡安全成為最近的熱話，大家都想保護自己的私隱，電話、電腦都講過，也是時候講講不太起眼，但又每天都用的路由器（router）。有沒有想過路由器也可以安裝VPN，保護全屋的裝置？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200722/GFLJOLFRIF5ZX7K6OMHLVP5TDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200722%2FGFLJOLFRIF5ZX7K6OMHLVP5TDU%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtBy8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=5a0dfccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200722%2FGFLJOLFRIF5ZX7K6OMHLVP5TDU%2F&h=190d1091\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200722/GFLJOLFRIF5ZX7K6OMHLVP5TDU/</a>"},{"pid":"22e6b798ea4e6dfd0243d1ad72d346d755814b3f","tid":2119560,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"最近一年，相信大家都已經了解到VPN（Virtual Private Network，虛擬私人網路）可以提高網絡連接的安全，但你又知不知路由器可以直接安裝VPN？資訊保安專家楊和生表示，如想家中所有上網裝置都有VPN保護，就可選擇在路由器上安裝VPN，「路由器就像一個互聯網的關口，無論是用網線還是無線連接，任何裝置如智能電視、雪櫃、洗衣機，只要經過這個路由器，就會得到同樣的VPN保護。」"},{"pid":"263019d764b2171639e867cf32c60dbb45baaa6a","tid":2119560,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"市面上的路由器和VPN供應商都有詳細的安裝方法，此功能大多是中高階路由器才會提供，並通過軟件OpenVPN實現，購買前記得搜尋路由器型號是否支援此功能。安裝亦很簡單，只需在VPN網頁下載OpenVPN的設定檔，再上傳至路由器的相關設定頁面，即可啓用VPN功能。不懂設定的阿媽、弟弟的手提電話都直接受到VPN保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"a58d54170be129fe48dd2d5091eae070671b4946","tid":2119560,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:22:35.000Z","msg":"楊和生建議，如家中有大量智能裝置，如機頂盒、智能門鎖等，想有保護，安裝在路由器是唯一選擇。相反大部份時間都是使用電話和電腦的話，就建議直接安裝在裝置上，因為可以時刻監察VPN連線狀況。"},{"pid":"73ec4f01ec1d0dfb1bb500e4c1ed9e80a56f5c8b","tid":2119560,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"楊和生補充：「大部份VPN都會提供稱為Kill Switch的功能，萬一裝置與VPN中斷連線，就會馬上斷開此裝置的互聯網連線。相反，<span class=\"x-large\"><em><span class=\"red\">將VPN設定在路由器上，就沒辦法提供Kill Switch，萬一路由器的VPN斷線，用家察覺不到繼續上網時，互聯網加密隨之也失去，身份就有機會暴露。</span></em></span>」有見及此，部份VPN供應商與第三方合作，提供改裝過的路由器，在路由器上實現Kill Switch功能。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. ASUS router 裝完第三方 firmware (ASUSWRT Merlin) 就有得用 kill switch，其他牌子就唔太清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/q_glossy,ret_img,w_404/https://www.vpnuniversity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Merlin-kill-switch.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_404%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.vpnuniversity.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FMerlin-kill-switch.png&h=982c7640&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d7f4a26c4a01fecba945383323a8609dd3ea14e","tid":2119560,"uid":258258,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"唔太明但pish"},{"pid":"656bf042d70a425f37c0b5139f7092d59defedad","tid":2119560,"uid":242795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"73ec4f01ec1d0dfb1bb500e4c1ed9e80a56f5c8b","tid":2119560,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"楊和生補充：「大部份VPN都會提供稱為Kill Switch的功能，萬一裝置與VPN中斷連線，就會馬上斷開此裝置的互聯網連線。相反，<span class=\"x-large\"><em><span class=\"red\">將VPN設定在路由器上，就沒辦法提供Kill Switch，萬一路由器的VPN斷線，用家察覺不到繼續上網時，互聯網加密隨之也失去，身份就有機會暴露。</span></em></span>」有見及此，部份VPN供應商與第三方合作，提供改裝過的路由器，在路由器上實現Kill Switch功能。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. ASUS router 裝完第三方 firmware (ASUSWRT Merlin) 就有得用 kill switch，其他牌子就唔太清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shortpixel.ai/client/q_glossy,ret_img,w_404/https://www.vpnuniversity.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Merlin-kill-switch.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shortpixel.ai%2Fclient%2Fq_glossy%2Cret_img%2Cw_404%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.vpnuniversity.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FMerlin-kill-switch.png&h=982c7640&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"有無用過Merlin嘅巴打分享下 <br />\n用ovpn profile 入咗VPN 之後會唔會成個網慢到pk<br />\n明明一部device 用嗰陣好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e59c5714c28f3ebf5581f374c634983a2bac416","tid":2119560,"uid":149306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:31:45.000Z","msg":"用緊mx5300<br />\n睇嚟只有l2tp可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f9531f17f21d9e9b8cad0c642dce1f3573b97c","tid":2119560,"uid":3480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"Hkbn用緊華為modem<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3a2f898b59592b2fc5e36b30ea7269b0509f27","tid":2119560,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1f9531f17f21d9e9b8cad0c642dce1f3573b97c","tid":2119560,"uid":3480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"Hkbn用緊華為modem<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"咁又點"},{"pid":"408bae164e5592802a239294ba56524d3e58d67e","tid":2119560,"uid":61954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d1f9531f17f21d9e9b8cad0c642dce1f3573b97c","tid":2119560,"uid":3480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:35:20.000Z","msg":"Hkbn用緊華為modem<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"邊間ISP唔係俾華為modem<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423c205857113137ed9d21884744b823a107a3d7","tid":2119560,"uid":3480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"408bae164e5592802a239294ba56524d3e58d67e","tid":2119560,"uid":61954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"qu